WEBVTT

00:01.335 --> 00:04.129
Previously on stargate atlantis...

00:04.463 --> 00:07.549
I could easily bring another 12 ships to the battle.

00:07.674 --> 00:10.219
12 ships, willing to fight shoulder to shoulder?

00:10.302 --> 00:13.096
For a chance to destroy the replicators once and for all?

00:13.222 --> 00:14.681
Of course.

00:15.599 --> 00:16.767
What did you do?

00:16.850 --> 00:18.852
- What are you referring to?
- There's a ship on the way.

00:18.977 --> 00:20.979
Ah, they picked up my signal.

00:21.104 --> 00:22.689
Subspace tracking device.

00:22.814 --> 00:23.565
Hello?

00:23.690 --> 00:24.983
Is anybody here?

00:25.067 --> 00:26.151
What happened?

00:26.276 --> 00:28.570
My people, they are gone.

00:28.695 --> 00:30.489
Searched the entire planet, no life-signs.

00:30.572 --> 00:32.031
I will find them.

00:32.156 --> 00:34.576
And we're going to help you, but you got to rest and get your strength back.

00:34.701 --> 00:37.079
Whoever did this will pay.

00:37.204 --> 00:39.790
I will make certain of it.

