00:50.217 --> 00:52.010
I'm so sorry, teyla.

00:52.552 --> 00:53.637
Kanaan was a good man.

00:53.762 --> 00:55.847
He would have made a wonderful father.

00:58.642 --> 01:01.478
I really thought I could save him.

01:01.561 --> 01:03.814
You did everything you could.

01:03.939 --> 01:06.191
That's all anybody can ask for.

01:06.650 --> 01:08.568
He's at peace now.

01:19.329 --> 01:20.789
All right.

01:21.331 --> 01:22.958
I'm ready.

02:11.631 --> 02:12.924
Teyla...

02:14.468 --> 02:15.135
teyla!

02:15.260 --> 02:16.261
He's still alive!

02:16.386 --> 02:17.846
Help me, teyla, please!

02:18.055 --> 02:18.847
Please help me!

02:18.972 --> 02:20.515
He's still alive! Let me go!

02:20.640 --> 02:21.892
Teyla, it's too late.

02:22.017 --> 02:23.977
Help me, teyla! Teyla!

02:24.102 --> 02:25.270
Teyla...

02:26.396 --> 02:28.648
teyla!

